# Get set up and oriented
docker build -t friendlyhello .

docker run -d -p 4000:80 friendlyhello

# 登录

docker login

# 对镜像打标签


# 服务
docker-compose.yml文件是一个YAML文件，用于定义Docker容器在生产过程中的行为
docker-compose.yml

```
version: "1"
services:
  web:
    image: shaonbean/nginx:latest
    deploy:
      replicas: 5
      resources:
        limits:
          cpus: "0.1"
          memory: 50M
      restart_policy:
        condition: on-failure
    ports:
      - "80:80"
    networks:
      - webnet
networks:
  webnet:
```

